# Design Document Rules

## GDD Requirements
Every system GDD under `design/gdd/` must include:
1. **Overview** — one-paragraph summary
2. **Core Mechanics** — how it works
3. **Player Experience** — what the player feels/does
4. **Balancing** — numbers, formulas, tuning knobs
5. **Edge Cases** — what happens when things go wrong
6. **Dependencies** — which other systems it touches
7. **Open Questions** — unresolved design decisions

## Narrative Docs
- Character descriptions must include: name, faction, motivation, barks, quest role
- Dialogue flow docs must reference the JSON file path

## Level Design
- Region docs must list all POIs with positions and gameplay purpose
- Include a rough spatial layout diagram (ASCII or reference image)
